Business description                     :
manufactures and sells processed seaweed and other kind of snacks, such as 
popcorn. Products can be divided into 5 main categories which can be categorized
as follows: 1) Crispy seaweed 2) Grilled seaweed 3) Tempura seaweed 4) Roasted
seaweed 5) Other products consist of Popcorn business, Snack and souvenir shop
business and Buttered & sugared toast and corn snack business.
Remark                                   :
